# **Design Rules — I-Medic Web (Vivid Calm Edition)**

## 🌈 Brand + Color (Apple-Inspired Vibrant Korean Palette)

**Concept:** Calm base, vivid emotion — inspired by Apple’s health visuals.
Use color to express life, trust, and warmth. Maintain balance: **75 % neutral / 20 % vivid / 5 % accent.**

### 🎨 Color Tokens

| Role            | Hex       | Usage                                             |
| --------------- | --------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| **Brand Blue**  | `#007AFF` | Main CTAs, hero background, trusted elements      |
| **Brand Dark**  | `#0047B2` | Hover / strong text accents                       |
| **Bright Red**  | `#FF3B30` | Highlights for vitality, alert, or emotional tone |
| **Coral Warm**  | `#FF6B6B` | Human, caring sections or hover gradients         |
| **Sky Light**   | `#EAF3FF` | Section backgrounds, dividers                     |
| **Mint Calm**   | `#6EE7B7` | Healing / recovery sections                       |
| **Butter Soft** | `#FFF4CE` | Wellness, comfort backgrounds                     |
| **Ink Text**    | `#0F172A` | Body text                                         |
| **Ink-Muted**   | `#1E293B` | Subtext                                           |
| **Line**        | `#E5E7EB` | Borders                                           |
| **Soft Base**   | `#FAFBFF` | Default page background                           |

> **Tip:** Never combine bright red and blue in the same component. Use one vivid per section.
> Max 2 accent hues visible per viewport.

### ✨ Gradient Presets

* **Hero Gradient:** `linear-gradient(180deg, #4DA3FF 0%, #007AFF 100%)`
* **Care Section:** `linear-gradient(180deg, #FFE6E6 0%, #FFFFFF 100%)`
* **Wellness Section:** `linear-gradient(180deg, #E9F3FF 0%, #FFFFFF 100%)`
* **Companion Section:** `linear-gradient(180deg, #E6FFF7 0%, #FFFFFF 100%)`

