## 🧭 Navigation Workflow

* Sticky header — logo left, center links: **Services, Programs, Pricing, How, Contact**
* Right side: **EN | BN**, WhatsApp CTA
* Mobile → hamburger → slide Sheet
* Smooth scroll with `scroll-margin-top: 80px`
* Active link underline in brand blue
* Floating WhatsApp icon bottom-right (mobile)

---

## 📱 Responsiveness

* Breakpoints: `sm 640`, `md 768`, `lg 1024`, `xl 1280`
* Test widths: 360×800, 390×844, 414×896, 768×1024, 1366×768, 1440×900, 1920×1080
* Rules:

  * Hero illustration hides <768px
  * Text lines ≤2 on small devices
  * 1–2–3 column progressive layout
  * Buttons wrap without overflow
  * Images stack with fade transitions

---

## ♿ Accessibility

* Contrast: 4.5 : 1 (body), 3 : 1 (large text)
* Visible focus ring (`outline-brand`)
* Touch targets ≥ 44×44 px
* Keyboard accessible navigation + FAQ accordion
* `aria-label` for WhatsApp & Call CTAs

---

## ✍️ Content Style

* Simple, clear, reassuring tone.
* Emphasize benefits first: *"Organized health data. Reliable home care. Transparent pricing."*
* Lists > long paragraphs
* Use numeric prices (BDT). Avoid hidden fees or jargon.

---

## ⚙️ Performance

* Lighthouse: Performance ≥ 90, Accessibility ≥ 95
* JS budget ≤ 170 KB gzip/page
* Use `next/image` with lazy loading
* Preload only essential fonts
* Avoid Lottie/video above fold
* Gradient hero replaces heavy media

---

## 🌐 i18n

* Strings via `t()`.
* English default, Bangla mirror keys (values can remain English for now).
* Prices always numeric (Latin digits).

---

## ✅ QA Checklist

* Navigation anchors scroll correctly on all devices
* WhatsApp/Call CTAs open correct links
* Plan prices consistent in both languages
* FAQ accordion accessible via keyboard
* Zero layout shift
* No console warnings
* No content overflow at any size

